<plot>Erez, A Lone Soldier in the Israeli army, gets a special short leave- his father arrives from the Netherlands to visit him. When he forgets his weapon on a ride, just as he is about to meet his father, he has no choice but to try and track it down. When all hope to find it is lost, Erez decides to report the missing weapon at the closest police station. However, He soon finds out that the station is located in the middle of an Arab village. Amal, a local policeman, leads the young soldier on a journey through the village in a desperate attempt to find the weapon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?101019</url></doc>
